description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. Totally non-scripted, all in front of a live audience, all broadcast live to members. Today's update is RD 1 of 4. This was January's live match, now edited for your enjoyment!
The Dragon and Lyla Storm take on Ariel X and Beretta James in brutal live Tag Team Sexual wrestling. The object: Get you opponent in a hold, then sexually molest the hell out of them for points. It's simple, now add in Tags and a Live audience and you have the most intense authentic lesbian wrestling in the world!
title: Dragon, Ariel, Beretta, Lyla: The hottest girl on the net battle in a non-scripted Tag Team Event!
